{"tid":1674304,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[認真文][國際線] 要資料整合隊後勤支援","createTime":"2019-10-25T06:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T07:03:18.000Z","uid":295525,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b08f31b3197330c7d217c55af60d22b38f37fb","tid":1674304,"uid":295525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"我係 Andy Li ，夢境出身，到之後喺幾單眾籌﹑關公廟﹑國際發聲度幫手，到咗九月因為美國又開聽證會聯合國又開人權會等等，唔夠手足同時去咁多個地方發聲，決定同妹妹 Beatrice 一齊除低面罩，去外國同議員﹑同民間組織﹑同聯合國﹑同記者講香港嘅故事﹑香港人嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\nPost 最低有片有相請 fact check 我嘅身份。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際線要資料整合隊後勤支援。</span><br />\n<br />\n而家不論同外國嘅邊位見面都好，其實不外乎幾條問題︰<br />\n<br />\n1. 請喺[x]分鐘內講，香港發生咩事。<br />\n2. 好，我支持你哋，實際上你想我哋[某國家﹑某組織﹑某人]做啲咩？<br />\n3. 請後補一份簡明嘅香港摘要，我哋四圍轉交俾人。<br />\n4. 請後補[x]證據，等我哋用嚟做嘢有根據。<br />\n<br />\n而香港場運動發展得極快，咪話本身國際線嘅手足已經唔夠人分身追新聞跟唔上，連我哋身在香港嘅都未必跟得上咁多條線。但而家一單新聞一單新聞咁send俾人哋的話人哋亦無時間同你睇哂佢，所以亦唔係就咁可以俾telegram channel佢睇。<br />\n<br />\n於是其一，我哋需要一份不停更新嘅香港情況摘要，等手足四圍爭取國際支持嗰陣可以交俾人哋用。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港嘅法律系統彰顯唔到公義，想告出國際的話，亦有各類正式非正式等嘅，包括有傳媒要資料，有議員要資料，聯合國手足要資料，國際人權律師要資料，即使想告上ICC都係嗰句，要資料。呢個亦已經有各類民間報告﹑各組織做過等，而家希望將呢啲料整合埋一齊，俾國際線手足用。<br />\n<br />\n於是其二，我哋需要收集各類侵犯人權呀，警暴呀等等嘅個案，一樣係有摘要同個案詳情咁。<br />\n<br />\n其中一樣其實外國會好大迴響同外國會好易做嘢嘅係，如果某單嘢牽涉到外國公民/機構，咁當地就名正言順去查，而唔駛淨係譴責遠處嘅香港。呢個唔止係明顯嘅武器供應商，仲包括例如某公司「只係」炒咗個參與罷工嘅人，但原來搵返佢母公司喺歐洲，咁歐洲議會嘅官員就可以喺歐洲郁佢。<br />\n<br />\n於是其三，我哋需要各類牽涉到外國嘅證據，交俾外國嗰邊做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n以上會交去邊度？外國議員﹑官員等；聯合國；國際人權律師；外國媒體；各民間組織；等等，其實只要幫香港人將我哋嘅故事講出嚟就得。<br />\n<br />\n我哋會公開模式運作，而家將香港人嘅故事講出嚟又無犯法。我哋整嘅報告會直接放上網頁 <a href=\"https://www.hkers.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkers.org%2F&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0d0f2331\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkers.org/</a> 度公開，任何手足都可以用。<br />\n<br />\n唔駛登入去google drive幫手一齊編輯個網頁︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1M7qqNJyd_HVpN6KYGJiZH0aKp8-25ib6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1M7qqNJyd_HVpN6KYGJiZH0aKp8-25ib6&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=29daa776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1M7qqNJyd_HVpN6KYGJiZH0aKp8-25ib6</a><br />\n<br />\n加入Telegram : @hkintlsupport<br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Fact Check 區</span><br />\n<br />\n小心假資訊﹑間諜等，唔好我講就信，尤其係有人問你攞資訊嗰啲。以下放低證據 fact check 我。<br />\n<br />\n關公廟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2EsM45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2EsM45.png&h=c3bcc6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯合國發言︰ no. 48, 01:28:31 開始。另外多謝蝗囯俾面連同奶共古巴同Eritrea連番參與，敵人想禁你聲表示做得好<br />\n<a href=\"http://webtv.un.org/search/item6-general-debate-28th-meeting-42nd-regular-session-human-rights-council/6088701440001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwebtv.un.org%2Fsearch%2Fitem6-general-debate-28th-meeting-42nd-regular-session-human-rights-council%2F6088701440001&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ca00fe1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://webtv.un.org/search/item6-general-debate-28th-meeting-42nd-regular-session-human-rights-council/6088701440001</a><br />\n<br />\n見法國議員Andr&eacute; Gattolin。遮咗嘅係法國當地手足，話說除面罩嘅係我哋唔係佢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7zP0to.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7zP0to.jpg&h=5d7ea8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要由香港飛過去發聲而唔係交俾當地手足？因為要帶證物。恭喜黑警揚威國際。<br />\n<br />\n到聯合國<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBKcYfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBKcYfc.jpg&h=0a13c58d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入法國議會，法國議員Dani&egrave;le Obono<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfOk68D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfOk68D.jpg&h=b0721f99&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"53eeceac73102a507ce9992e053286e3f3ba8d1d","tid":1674304,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(代POST)【本土X國際戰線】鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659927</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌傳送門﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=d07a3a75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"3e17ebdb9f654788b0f78d7f75ebd94630b0b64b","tid":1674304,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"提大家今個星期六日有咩活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期六 10 &middot; 26 醫護抗暴 - 醫療專職集會</strong></span><br />\n- 18:00 遮打花園 [已獲不反對通知書]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 <br />\n追究警暴 守護民眾記者 守護穆斯林</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 自由之鶴追悼會</strong></span><br />\n- 16:00 - 20:00 觀塘海濱公園"},{"pid":"1e44ced37b32ae5961916efb1cb579d846846951","tid":1674304,"uid":295525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"1aa38dcdbaa3455a51f49181f0922fa4bc1f11bd","tid":1674304,"uid":295525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"認真文總係推唔起"},{"pid":"d60037146887f575de0ee0b89847d465193b259a","tid":1674304,"uid":295525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"P牌今日開唔到新post，唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n呢個資料庫同時會交俾國際人權律師︰<br />\n<br />\n國際人權律師出手，話如果香港人收集到資料同個案，就可以交俾佢哋去睇有無得做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n律師列表︰<br />\n- William Bourdon (France, Human Rights lawyer, Snowden / Lula)<br />\n- Abderrahim Jama&iuml; (Morocco, Human Rights lawyer, former President of the Bar)<br />\n- Valeska Teixeira Zanin Martins (Brazil, Lula&rsquo;s lawer)<br />\n- Vanni Ceola (Italy, Human Rights lawyer)<br />\n- Baltasar Garz&oacute;n Real (Spain, Former judge / international crimes / ILOCAD)<br />\n- Mamadou Konat&eacute; (Mali, Former Minister of Justice)<br />\n- Christophe Marchand (Belgium, Human Rights lawyer, Assange&rsquo;s lawyer)<br />\n- Vincent Warren (USA, CCR Executive Director - en attente)<br />\n<br />\n請先自行睇呢班律師背景，確保唔係鬼。"},{"pid":"ceea24bd99dcfa8da2ff0bf71d1008c826ba3922","tid":1674304,"uid":194119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ffe22ac04bfe4a19a412d2fb31f1341ea6a22e94","tid":1674304,"uid":295525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"1c87e352ea990ae0ab04b93472dc1d776b55aa66","tid":1674304,"uid":109544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8121fc3e09d3bb0b148fba5805e16d24dbb487df","tid":1674304,"uid":109544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c71a9cc8589f21542bc49b79950564f1dae87833","tid":1674304,"uid":298585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56daf8c8c1112f418738d8856034236acede57f5","tid":1674304,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMvDbNv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMvDbNv.gif&h=fcf15a75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4570c0ac029aab8abea3669993b4995fa58defc","tid":1674304,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cb418dda35c982d40cdaa9e4058ef37ecbca1e","tid":1674304,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5c394105f98aa36f6d05a72a78f17a63566f19ad","tid":1674304,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1048599351028b738cbab5ac14ac2c0cf348bd80","tid":1674304,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:32:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10月26日</span></strong></span><br />\n「醫民同行. 共抗警暴」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">遮打集會1800</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hf293f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhf293f3.jpg&h=48e668cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月27日</span></span></strong><br />\n「追究警暴  連繫穆斯林<br />\n守護民眾  與記者同行」<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>梳士巴利花園 1500</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvA0quw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvA0quw.jpg&h=7052ebf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11月2日</span></span></strong>&nbsp;<br />\n「求援國際 堅守自治 」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式維園集會1500</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG0fYM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG0fYM3.jpg&h=a82afeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情參閱：<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=dfb1a434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a>"},{"pid":"fdc11654ae26cc54607c4b8e3b8ff3ddc2123af9","tid":1674304,"uid":295525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1279da3304e15d6cf225a9ba57a0d6d61db0e25b","tid":1674304,"uid":21965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:45:30.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2121b1b6100f4ab42229e1c4005afc903937eefe","tid":1674304,"uid":21965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:46:10.000Z","msg":"認真文，大家幫手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3e0a7e8d2e9fe16165322c57774fbacf24abb6","tid":1674304,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUPo8oT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUPo8oT.gif&h=0b30e983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9d2579a975dd55fccf96c41b19a69f648412dcc","tid":1674304,"uid":312860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77a40f6c4a70343c69163a23e5a931a0a7c4373","tid":1674304,"uid":118773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"4c296708182f997fbce9420c730b012dc981a910","tid":1674304,"uid":45795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"99ca4844150caeb1e5594337ff88c8841bcba98b","tid":1674304,"uid":198011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"推～～～～～"},{"pid":"a667f0df6408838ce9014a2b484b6d38f4f7bd8d","tid":1674304,"uid":9184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}